    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad klausija wiſſi Leeli-Kungi/ un wiſſi Laudis/ kaſ febo Derribu bij peezehmuschi/\nun atlaide ikkatrs fawu Kalpu\nun fawu Kalponi fwabbadus/\ntà ka tee wairs ne liktu few no\nteem kalpoht/ ta klausija tee/ un\natlaide tohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tee atgreesahs pehz\nto/ un likte tohs Kalpus un tahs\nKalpones nahkt atpakkat/ ko tee\nbij fwabbadus atlaiduschi/ un\npeede tohs par Kalpeem un par\nKalponehim buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz notikte ta KUNGGA Wahrdz us Jeremiju no ta KUNGGA/ kas fazziia:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta fakka tas KUNGS/\ntas Israëta Deews : Es eftmu\nweenu Derribu darrijs ar juhseem\nTehweem/ tai Deena/ kad es\ntohs iſwedde no Egiptes-Semmes/ no ta Wehrgu-Naimma/\nun fazziiju:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ap feptixo Gaddo Gallu\nbuhs jums atlaist ikweens fa-wu Brahti/ kas weens Eebreëris\nirr/ kas tew pahrdohts irr/ un\ntew feſchus Gaddus kalpojs irr/\nun tew buhs winnu fwabbadu\nno tewim atlaist: Bet juhſu\nTehwi manni ne klausija/ un ne\natgreese fawas Austis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta bijat juhs nu scho-deen atgreesuschees / un darrijschi/ kas teefa bija mannas Az-zis/ isfaukdami Swabbadibu/\nikweens preekſch fawa Tuwaka/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet juhs effat atpakkat greesuschees/ un mannu Wahrdz faqabntifcht / un atpakkat aizi-najſchi ikweens fawu Kalpu/ un ikweens fawu Kalponi / ko juhs bijat fwabbadu laiduschi pehz winno Prahta / un efteet tohs speedutcht jums par Kalpeem un par Kalponehim buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht ta fakka tas KUNGS: Juhs ne eftat man-ni klausijſchi/ ka juhs buhtut Swabbadibu isfaukſchi ikkatrs preekſch fawa Brahta/ un ikkatrs preekſch fawa Tuwaka. Rangi/tad isfauzu es prett jums Swab-badibu / jakka tas KUNGS: Uhs Sohbinn/ us Mehri/ un us Baddu/ un nodohschu juhs eelfch Nenostahſchanas wiffas Semmes Walstitbas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es nodohschu tohs Wihrus/ kas mannu Derribu tre vahrkahpuschi/ kas ne irr stipri-najschi tahs Derribas Wahrdus/ ko tee manna Preekſcha irr darrijschi/ itt ka to Telfu/ ko tee diwejōs Gabbalōs bij zirtufchi/\nun starp teem Gabbaleem zaur gabje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tohs Leel-Kungus no Juhda/un Jerusalemes Leel-Kungus / tohs Kambar-Junkurus/ un Preesterus/ un wiffus Lau-dis tahs Semmes/ kas starp ta\n"
    }
  ],
